{"about_the_game":"<strong>Synopsis:</strong><br><br>A month has passed since the events of the first game. Pegasus-5 crew now find themselves on planet Talann. What was planned as a temporary overnight stay turned into something more. After a terrorist attack in the city, the government had suspended all traffic in and out of the country and put more police on the streets in order to catch those responsible. The Pegasus-5 crew now find themselves stuck in an unfamiliar city and gradually drawn into dangerous events occurring in the city. With stakes increasing each day and inaction becoming less of an option, between pressure from a mysterious hacker, increased security on the streets, and mercenary groups trying to achieve their own goals, Edan and his allies have to get involved and start making choices. <br><br><strong>General Features:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> A sequel to Pegasus-5: Gone Astray, following a new plot taking place in a politically corrupt cyberpunk city.<br></li><li> Narrative point of view changes between two main protagonists.<br></li><li> Beautifully rendered 3D images during romantic and key story scenes.<br></li><li> Trust, Morale, and Romance building with your allies.<br></li><li> Choose character specialisations at the start to provide some alternative ways of solving tasks and problems.<br></li><li> Choices have consequences on the future events and endings.</li></ul>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"I never asked for this ","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1633740/c24f30f7938030c3a02ebcdb42b7859013d851ad.jpg"},{"name":"That\u2019s speeding! ","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1633740/72739858c92ab09bff620d80dbf5e0c874e342c7.jpg"},{"name":"Raid Runner ","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1633740/1226120441456d4206e3eab7ea5837dbf7ce85ae.jpg"},{"name":"Mission Impossible ","path":"https://cdn.